* And begin *

39:10.380 --> 39:14.520
* When does it rise *

39:15.450 --> 39:18.170
* Again... *

39:18.370 --> 39:20.340
How'd it happen, Sarah?

39:20.540 --> 39:22.870
I pressed him

39:23.070 --> 39:27.540
about the women he was supposed
to have taken advantage of.

39:27.740 --> 39:29.550
I pressed him about...

39:29.750 --> 39:32.220
the circumstances
of Diane's death.

39:32.420 --> 39:34.020
He became enraged

39:34.220 --> 39:36.220
that I wouldn't take
his answers at face value,

39:36.420 --> 39:38.020
that I kept
pressing him.

39:38.220 --> 39:41.160
I did what I'd learned to do
as a prosecutor.

39:41.360 --> 39:43.860
Who suggested you meet here?
I did.

39:44.060 --> 39:45.560
I thought
he wouldn't get violent

39:45.760 --> 39:47.500
if we met in a public place

39:47.700 --> 39:49.750
where there
were cameras.

39:50.650 --> 39:52.040
I was wrong about that.

39:52.240 --> 39:53.170
What'd he do?

39:53.370 --> 39:54.640
He put his hands around my neck,

39:54.840 --> 39:56.870
and he started to choke me,
and I wasn't going

39:57.070 --> 40:00.080
to let him do to me
what he did to Diane.

40:00.280 --> 40:02.080
So I shot him.

40:02.280 --> 40:04.150
* Rise again... *

40:04.350 --> 40:06.530
Was it self-defense, Sarah?

40:08.130 --> 40:12.570
I think it would qualify
as self-defense, yes.

40:14.070 --> 40:16.360
You understand we're going
to have to arrest you now?

40:16.560 --> 40:18.260
I do understand.

40:18.460 --> 40:20.780
I'm familiar with the process.

40:23.350 --> 40:27.690
* Rise... *

40:32.660 --> 40:35.650
She says it was self-defense.
You buy it?

40:35.850 --> 40:38.350
A good prosecutor could
probably punch holes in it.

40:38.550 --> 40:40.350
But would they want to?

40:40.550 --> 40:43.020
Would they just want
to let it go?

